OL,3,C'Once in a generation' plan approved
OL,4,Cfor new South West city district
OL,6,FUpdated plans to build 6,500 new homes
OL,7,Fon a former airfield on the outskirts
OL,8,Fof Bristol have been approved.
OL,10,FSouth Gloucestershire Council has
OL,11,Fgranted permission for revised plans
OL,12,Ffrom YTL Developments to redevelop the
OL,13,Fformer Filton Airfield site.
OL,15,FDevelopers say the regeneration is a
OL,16,F"once-in-a-generation opportunity."
