OL,3,C'Once in a generation' plan approved
OL,4,Cfor new South West city district
OL,6,FThe new neighbourhood includes shops,
OL,7,Foffices, three new schools and
OL,8,FBrabazon Park, a new public open space
OL,9,Fthat will be equivalent in size to
OL,10,FBristol's Castle Park.
OL,12,FThere will also be up to 2,000 beds
OL,13,Ffor student accommodation and up to 3
OL,14,Fmillion square feet of commercial
OL,15,Fspace - enough to support 30,000 jobs.
OL,17,FOriginally the application included
OL,18,F2,500 homes, but that has now
OL,19,Fincreased.
