OL,3,C'Once in a generation' plan approved
OL,4,Cfor new South West city district
OL,6,FImproved transport links are being
OL,7,Flooked at to support the development
OL,8,Fand more than #100 million is already
OL,9,Fbeing invested in the local transport
OL,10,Fnetwork.
OL,12,FIt's hoped a new rail station will
OL,13,Fconnect the neighbourhood to Bristol
OL,14,FTemple Meads in less than 15 minutes.
OL,16,FSeb Loyn, Planning & Development
OL,17,FDirector for YTL Developments, said:
OL,18,F"The approval of the new Masterplan
OL,19,Ffor Brabazon is a once-in-a-generation
OL,20,Fopportunity.
