OL,3,C'Once in a generation' plan approved
OL,4,Cfor new South West city district
OL,6,F"It will transform not just North
OL,7,FBristol and South Gloucestershire, but
OL,8,Fthe entirety of the West of England.
OL,10,F"The region desperately needs more
OL,11,Fhomes. Brabazon will deliver 6,500,
OL,12,Fwith over 1,700 being affordable.
OL,14,F"This decision paves the way for YTL
OL,15,FDevelopments to build the new homes,
OL,16,Foffices, schools and community
OL,17,Ffacilities we all need, and to do so
OL,18,Fin a way that is environmentally and
OL,19,Feconomically sustainable."
