OL,3,C'Once in a generation' plan approved
OL,4,Cfor new South West city district
OL,6,F"The development will help reduce
OL,7,Freliance on car travel with Metrobus
OL,8,Fand local buses serving the area along
OL,9,Fwith the train station which already
OL,10,Fhas secured planning permission.
OL,12,F"A community hub and health care
OL,13,Ffacility will also be provided, along
OL,14,Fwith parks, lakes and open spaces,
OL,15,Fwith over 3,500 trees planted on the
OL,16,Fsite."
OL,18,FThe first homes at Brabazon are due to
OL,19,Fcompleted in 2025.
